thread.title: Mexico's Cemex posts 50 pct jump in 2nd-qtr profit
thread.title_full: Mexico's Cemex posts 50 pct jump in 2nd-qtr profit | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Mexico's Cemex posts 50 pct jump in 2nd-qtr profit
text:
MEXICO CITY, July 22 Mexico's Cemex, one of the world's largest cement companies, on Wednesday reported a 50 percent jump in second-quarter net profit compared to the same period a year earlier.
The company said net profit in the April-June period was $114 million, compared to $76 million a year earlier. (Reporting by Christine Murray , Editing by Franklin Paul)
